# RTK frontdoor

All Claude shell work enters through the profile-owned RTK binary. The active
command is `/home/flexnetos/.nix-profile/toolbin/rtk`; repository commands use
the repository-required RTK adapter and profile Nushell.

```nu
rtk --version
rtk verify
rtk gain
rtk proxy -- /home/flexnetos/.nix-profile/toolbin/nu -l -c "command"
```

The Claude `PreToolUse` hook routes Bash-tool requests through `rtk hook claude`.
Do not bypass that hook with an alternate binary, shell owner, or raw payload.
